#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "thag2.11:4.1"
msgid "2.11. Mahācundattheragāthā"
msgstr "2.11. Mahācunda"

#. </h1></div><blockquote class="gatha"><p><a class="sc" id="1"></a><a
#. class="vns" id="vns141"></a><a class="vnp" id="vnp141"></a><a class="pts"
#. id="pts20"></a>
msgctxt "thag2.11:5.1"
msgid "“Sussūsā sutavaddhanī,"
msgstr "It’s from wishing to learn that learning grows;"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag2.11:5.2"
msgid "sutaṃ paññāya vaddhanaṃ;"
msgstr "when you’re learned, wisdom grows;"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag2.11:5.3"
msgid "Paññāya atthaṃ jānāti,"
msgstr "by wisdom, you know the goal;"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag2.11:5.4"
msgid "ñāto attho sukhāvaho."
msgstr "knowing the goal brings happiness."

#. HTML: </p><p><a class="sc" id="2"></a> <a class="vns" id="vns142"></a><a
#. class="vnp" id="vnp142"></a>
msgctxt "thag2.11:6.1"
msgid "Sevetha pantāni senāsanāni,"
msgstr "You should frequent remote lodgings"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag2.11:6.2"
msgid "Careyya saṃyojanavippamokkhaṃ;"
msgstr "and practice to be released from fetters."

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag2.11:6.3"
msgid "Sace ratiṃ nādhigaccheyya tattha,"
msgstr "If you don’t find enjoyment there,"

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "thag2.11:6.4"
msgid "Saṃghe vase rakkhitatto satimā”ti."
msgstr "live in the Saṅgha, self-guarded and mindful."

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p class="endsutta">
